Text: I wasn't getting the option to browse for the key file.  So I tried option 2 as instructed below.  After the 11111-11111 code failed, I selected the Trial Code option and clicked next, got the error code and the following window had the option to Browse.  The key I entered only has 355 days left, so I got burnt for a day =(
I think the key element to my success was being offline.  Had I been online it would've processed the 30 day trial Key and gave me that many days or less.
